{"tid":2119450,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"著名男偶像B組合、女偶像T組合FANS 將垃圾當成捐贈品","createTime":"2020-07-22T06:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T06:14:30.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e563196addb975252d047f92787c9094eee29def","tid":2119450,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0OsAL5G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0OsAL5G.jpg&h=e3ff889e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ufjCZqG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FufjCZqG.jpg&h=721d9d17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麻浦區廳內發現大量藝人歌手專輯&hellip;&hellip;與企劃公司囤積&bull;勾結關係疑惑<br />\n在首爾某行政機關發現了大量著名歌手的專輯，引發了囤積、與藝人企劃公司的勾結關係的疑惑。<br />\n本月15日，記者來到位於首爾市麻浦區廳的地下停車場。在這裡發現了大量裝有歌手唱片和專輯的箱子。<br />\n被發現的專輯中有現在活躍活動的著名男性愛豆B組合、女性愛豆T組合和solo等多數歌手的專輯。<br />\n麻浦區廳方面表示&ldquo;只是唱片會方面捐贈的&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.well-buying.com/files/attach/images/14690/258/084/b343b032a6a01498408e1d3007b50fac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.well-buying.com%2Ffiles%2Fattach%2Fimages%2F14690%2F258%2F084%2Fb343b032a6a01498408e1d3007b50fac.jpg&h=2180ac1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.well-buying.com/files/attach/images/14690/258/084/1efd33019dd908a6329ccdd267bbd88b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.well-buying.com%2Ffiles%2Fattach%2Fimages%2F14690%2F258%2F084%2F1efd33019dd908a6329ccdd267bbd88b.jpg&h=f5c15eb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻浦青少年中心方面表示：&ldquo;勾結關係並不屬實...收到專輯捐贈後，分享給青少年&rdquo;<br />\n市立麻浦青少年中心否認了偶像專輯囤積嫌疑。<br />\n市立麻浦青少年中心方面22日表示：&ldquo;海外K-POP粉絲購買專輯時，往往只拿走小卡扔掉CD，因此唱片流通企業Ktown4u與粉絲們協商後進行捐贈專輯&rdquo;，&ldquo;捐贈的專輯會分發給利用設施、慶典、分享活動等的青少年&rdquo;。<br />\n接著補充道：&ldquo;從今年6月開始，由於新冠肺炎的影響，中心沒能開放，專輯庫存積壓&rdquo;，&ldquo;因為數量太多，所以暫時將專輯放在麻浦區廳地下停車場&rdquo;。<br />\n之前某媒體當天報導稱在麻浦區廳地下停車場發現了大量偶像專輯。據報導，相關機關的地下停車場中有大量裝有偶像專輯的箱子，金額達數千萬韓元，並提出了與演藝企劃公司有勾結的疑惑。<br />\n但是，這並不是事實。<br />\n麻浦區廳相關人士當天也表示&ldquo;對報導不准確的事實表示遺憾&rdquo;，&ldquo;將要求進行更正報導等&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n塞D垃圾比人當做左善事 笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7b85600b8d78c9d8dbfe0499b610391987a19a","tid":2119450,"uid":132174,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:11:06.000Z","msg":"BOYZ TWINS"},{"pid":"33386626074f76ce0fffa38781a70aff89e63fc4","tid":2119450,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea7b85600b8d78c9d8dbfe0499b610391987a19a","tid":2119450,"uid":132174,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:11:06.000Z","msg":"BOYZ TWINS"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f5720dabaf09cf032aba9ea070fe34abe02a0a","tid":2119450,"uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ea7b85600b8d78c9d8dbfe0499b610391987a19a","tid":2119450,"uid":132174,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:11:06.000Z","msg":"BOYZ TWINS"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4F6rGJH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4F6rGJH.gif&h=cc3fdfd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8cb6061b3a453b68461bc413645767c45c6e193a","tid":2119450,"uid":33508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea7b85600b8d78c9d8dbfe0499b610391987a19a","tid":2119450,"uid":132174,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:11:06.000Z","msg":"BOYZ TWINS"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:14:30.000Z","msg":"唔怪得淨係要閃卡"}]}